sudo apt update -y
sudo apt install ansible -y
inventory location - /etc/ansible/hosts
ansible -m ping all - this will lists all nodes
ansible <nodename> -m setup ---to know the node information
scp -i key.pem key.pem ubuntu@masterIP :~ --- this will copy server key from node to master if we enter this command on any worker node
use:
apt module to install any web server, to update the system
file module to create, delete or remove file
git module to deploy a code
copy to copy files
service to restart nginx or any web server


we use condition if we are using multiple types of machines 
